name: THE FEARZ - Early Bird Pack (Founder's Edition, Release 1)
description:
THE FEARZ UNIVERSE is a collection of unique NFTs living on the Tezos Blockchain. The Early Bird Pack grants you one unique THE FEARZ collectible of the Founder's Edition that carries the Early Bird tag. There are over 100 unique traits. The Founder's Edition contains 1,000 THE FEARZ. 

In order to open the Early Bird Pack send it to OpenPack.TheFearz.tez. You'll receive a randomly picked unique (1/1) THE FEARZ collectible within 24 hours. 

Follow us on Twitter @TheFearzNFT
